<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-08-02T09:00:00-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-08-02T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-02T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Surface Pro 11 评测：离梦想非常近</title><content type="html">&lt;p>;微软最新的二合一设备完全基于 Arm，它是该公司最接近地将笔记本电脑的强大功能与平板电脑的电池寿命和灵活性融为一体的产品。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24191243/microsoft-surface-pro-11-oled-review&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24191243/microsoft-surface-pro-11-oled-review" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24191243/microsoft-surface-pro-11-oled-review</id><author><name>内森·爱德华兹</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-02T08:24:19-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-02T08:24:19-04:00</updated><title> AI音乐初创公司称侵犯版权只是摇滚乐</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;该图像显示了一个稍微不平衡的机器人面孔网格，上面有包含音符的语音气泡。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/_2M4HUGJ7a0y_sAF9fFzhD8Pg7Y=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73497514/STK467_AI_Music.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge / Shutterstock&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;sGSVOl&quot;>;在遭受版权侵权诉讼几周后，人工智能音乐初创公司 Suno 和 Udio 现在指控了提起诉讼的唱片公司试图扼杀音乐行业内的竞争。两家公司都承认使用受版权保护的材料&lt;a href=&quot;https://fingfx.thomsonreuters.com/gfx/legaldocs/zjvqymadevx/USA%20COURT%20MUSIC%20COPYRIGHTS%20sunoanswer.pdf&quot;>;分别训练他们的音乐生成人工智能模型&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://fingfx.thomsonreuters.com/gfx/legaldocs/dwpkzyjqdvm/USA%20COURT%20MUSIC%20COPYRIGHTS%20udioanswer.pdf&quot;>;法律备案&lt;/a>;，认为这样做是根据合理使用原则合法。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;FiSWYV&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/24/24184710/riaa-ai-lawsuit-suno -udio-copyright-umg-sony-warner&quot;>;美国唱片业协会 (RIAA) 于 6 月对 Suno 和 Udio 提起诉讼&lt;/a>;，该协会代表环球音乐集团 (UMG)、索尼音乐娱乐公司和华纳唱片公司。这两起案件均指控 Suno 和 Udio 侵犯版权，涉及 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/24/24185181/listen-to-the-ai-songs-music-labels-say -violate-their-copyright&quot;>;未经许可的声音复制...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/2/24211842/ai -music-riaa-版权诉讼-suno-udio-fair-use&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/2/24211842/ai-music-riaa-copyright-lawsuit-suno-udio-fair-use" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/2/24211842/ai-music-riaa-copyright-lawsuit-suno-udio-fair-use</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-02T08:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-02T08:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Humble Games 裁员让独立工作室陷入不确定状态</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Bō 的屏幕截图：青莲之路。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/SoJP4ZLtZHVJgoi1If8Llh2l3TA=/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73497447/ss_bb71f73647e517256b7 2708c60a3649e1470931a.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Squid Shock Studios&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;MvpBAw&quot;>;Humble Games“重组”并据报道解雇了 36 人的团队 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/2024/7/23/24204641/beloved-indie-game-publisher-humble-games-has-reportedly-laid-off-all-staff-without-warning&quot;>;上周&lt;/a>;。该发行商是 IGN 旗下 Humble Bundle 的一部分，开始帮助开发者发布游戏 &lt;a href=&quot;https://developer.humblebundle.com/post/157036461841/humble-bundle-launches-multi-platform-publishing&quot; >;2017 年&lt;/a>;并发布了&lt;em>;Slay the Spire&lt;/em>;和&lt;em>;Signalis&lt;/em>;等著名游戏。裁员带来的影响使得与发行商合作的开发者对未来游戏的许多计划感到不确定，从而使他们的控制台端口处于危险之中。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;PDP03E&quot;>;Amir Fassihi，《Dead Mage》工作室总监，正在开发的《Wizard of Legend 2》背后的团队担心重组可能会影响他们的项目。 “我们不想做出任何改变，”Fassihi 告诉 &lt;em>;The Verge&lt;/em>;。 “但是，我们不确定我们将被迫做出哪些改变，因为发行商中的每个人都...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/2 /24211410/humble-games-layoffs-indie-studios-uncertainty&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/2/24211410/humble-games-layoffs-indie-studios-uncertainty" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/2/24211410/humble-games-layoffs-indie-studios-uncertainty</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-02T07:30:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-02T07:30:00-04:00</updated><title>泵和特朗普</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;小 RFK、唐纳德·特朗普和比特币大会对象被吸入漩涡的照片插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7eju0Lr5h8PkWwvjN813K0yesfg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73497426/247202_Bitcoin_conference2_CVirginia.0 .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge； Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;走进 2024 年比特币大会由 MAGA 推动的狂热梦想。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24211345/ bitcoin-conference-2024-nashville-trump-maga-crypto&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24211345/bitcoin-conference-2024-nashville-trump-maga-crypto" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24211345/bitcoin-conference-2024-nashville-trump-maga-crypto</id><author><name>盖比·德尔·瓦莱</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-02T05:49:59-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-02T05:49:59-04:00</updated><title>英伟达因市场主导地位面临两项美国司法部反垄断调查</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Ndivia 徽标的矢量拼贴画。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/y15z23OY3TnwZZwnl7fRY7CSQRM=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73497319/STK083_B_NVIDIA_A.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;RYEiwJ&quot;>;据报道，美国司法部 (DOJ) 对 Nvidia 发起了两项单独的调查，涉及这家计算巨头专注于人工智能的反垄断担忧商业往来。第一项调查，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.politico.com/news/2024/08/01/feds-nvidia-ai-deal-chips-00172322&quot;>;由&lt;em>;Politico&lt;/em>;报道&lt;/a>;，将看到司法部检查&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/24/24139331/nvidia-buys-gpu-management-software-company-run-ai&quot;>; Nvidia 收购了 Run:ai，&lt;/a>;，而第二个，据 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theinformation.com/articles/nvidia-faces-doj-antitrust-probe-over-complaints-from 报道-rivals&quot;>;&lt;em>;信息&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;将评估 Nvidia 是否滥用其在人工智能芯片领域的主导地位来阻止客户使用竞争产品。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;R422J6&quot;>;4 月据报道，英伟达斥资 7 亿美元收购了专门从事 GPU 管理软件的以色列初创公司 Run:ai。虽然围绕 Run:ai 收购的具体担忧尚未披露，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/7/19/23800545/khan-ftc-doj-justice-antitrust-guidelines- meta-amazon&quot;>;美国&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/7/13/23793969/adobe-figma-merger-acquisition-uk-cma-regulator-investigation &quot;>;国际监管机构&lt;/a>;最近密切关注大型科技收购的问题...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/2/24211810 /nvidia-doj-antitrust-probes-ai-market-dominance&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/2/24211810/nvidia-doj-antitrust-probes-ai-market-dominance" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/2/24211810/nvidia-doj-antitrust-probes-ai-market-dominance</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-01T19:34:48-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-01T19:34:48-04:00</updated><title>英特尔崩溃的第 13 代和第 14 代 CPU 获得额外两年的保修期</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hcAIcD-2iHJOoRxuOQSruT81EMw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73496896/acastro_STK094_03.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Afn0xC&quot;>;尽管有 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/2024/7/26/24206529/intel-13th-14th-gen-crashing-instability-cpu-Voltage-qa&quot;>;没有修复英特尔崩溃的第 13 代和第 14 代英特尔酷睿处理器&lt;/a>;，该公司正在尝试通过将保修期延长两年来为那些遇到可能损坏芯片的客户提供更好的服务。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Y2pNCT&quot;>;“英特尔致力于确保所有拥有或正在使用芯片的客户目前在第 13 代和/或第 14 代桌面处理器上遇到不稳定症状的用户在交换过程中受到支持。”英特尔的 Thomas Hannaford 在向 The Verge 发表的一份声明中写道。 “我们支持我们的产品，在未来几天，我们将分享有关盒装英特尔酷睿第 13 代和第 14 代台式机处理器两年延长保修支持的更多详细信息。”&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float -left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;BSu3Dk&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;英特尔正在裁员超过 15,000 名员工，并将停止‘非必要工作’&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/1/24210656/intel-is-laying-off-over- 10000 名员工并将削减 100 亿成本&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;1XXw5b&quot;>;英特尔的盒装 CPU 已经拥有 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/support/articles/000024255/processors.html#:~:text=Warranty%20policy%20for%20Intel%C2%AE%20Boxed% 20处理器，Intel%20提供%20a%20product%20replacement&quot;>;三年...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/ 1/24211616/intel-crashing-13th-14th-gen-cpus-warranty-two-more-years&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/1/24211616/intel-crashing-13th-14th-gen-cpus-warranty-two-more-years" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/1/24211616/intel-crashing-13th-14th-gen-cpus-warranty-two-more-years</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-01T18:30:58-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-01T18:30:58-04:00</updated><title>网络中立性已冰冻</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;扩音器的照片插图，其中有 wifi 符号。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ZaSLiTLHXexFeFkybwJwuzh_PVE=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73496838/STK473_NET_NEUTRALITY_CVIRGINIA_D.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 绘制 |图片来自Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ldbsO2&quot;>;在第六巡回上诉法院阻止该规则生效后，网络中立性被正式搁置。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;yH1bAX &quot;>;法院批准暂缓执行，延长了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/15/24199126/net-neutrality-rules-temporarily-halted-sixth- Circuit&quot;>;之前的临时禁令暂停&lt;/a>;。这一次，网络中立性将被阻止，直到法院在审查反对该规则的宽带提供商的请愿书后做出相反的决定。评审团写道，这些互联网服务提供商 (ISP) 成功地表明，他们很可能会在挑战中取得成功。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;v7hhN1&quot;>;“美国公众想要一个快速、开放的互联网联邦通信委员会主席杰西卡·罗森沃塞尔 (Jessica Rosenworcel) 在一份关于暂缓执行的声明中表示。 “第六巡回法院今天的决定是一个挫折，但我们不会放弃争取网络中立性的斗争。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;fS6N59&quot;>;T...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/1/24211570/net-neutrality-sixth-circ-stay-blocked-fcc&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/1/24211570/net-neutrality-sixth-circuit-stay-blocked-fcc" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/1/24211570/net-neutrality-sixth- Circuit-stay-blocked-fcc</id><author><name>劳伦·费纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-01T18:29:33-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-01T18:29:33-04:00</updated><title> NZXT 将租用全套游戏电脑，但成本增加得很快</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;来自 NZXT.com 网站的图像，显​​示其中一台可以通过 Flex 订阅租用的台式电脑，以及该计划的基本详细信息。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/K59VzicS1YV4BMqDd2DBv8Fsv8g=/11x0:1631x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73496829/1722442439_1920x1080_ nzxt_flex_enen.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：NZXT&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;7sz5sh&quot;>;想要进入电脑游戏领域，但感觉生活中没有足够的昂贵订阅？台式电脑制造商和零售商 NZXT &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fnzxt.com%2Fnews%2Fflex&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp ;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F8%2F1%2F24211490%2Fnzxt-flex-desktop-gaming-pc-rental-service-subscription-nvidia-gpu-games&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;每月只需 59 美元即可向您运送整个游戏装备&lt;/a>; - 只要您提供自己的鼠标、键盘和显示器。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot; t7AJVL&quot;>;Flex 订阅计划已经推出至少几个月了，基于 &lt;a href=